es.unizar.smartcampuz.model

Interface EntityRepository<T,ID extends java.io.Serializable>

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ReportRepository, ReservationRepository, WorkerRepository

    public interface EntityRepository<T,ID extends java.io.Serializable>
    Generic repository for entities. Based on CRUDRepository and used to reverse dependencies.
